# HR ERP orchestrator

**Process enforcement:** [`.cursor/hooks.json`](../hooks.json) (`GOVERNANCE_HOOK_MODE=shadow|enforce`). **Domain invariants:** [repo-boundaries.mdc](repo-boundaries.mdc).

**Operator guide:** [cursor-3-native-runtime.md](../../docs/meta/cursor-3-native-runtime.md) · Manifest v3: [`.cursor/governance/governance-manifest.yaml`](../governance/governance-manifest.yaml)

## Quick start

1. Classify tier: `npm run governance:lint`
2. Emit DAG JSON: `node scripts/governance-lint.mjs plan --json`
3. Parallel lanes: `/multitask` (scout+architect, sentinel+verifier)
4. DDL isolation: `/worktree` + custodian → builder
5. PR stub: `npm run governance:pr-body` or hook `stop` output

## Native commands (ADR 0011)

| Lane | Command |
|------|---------|
| scout + architect | `/multitask` |
| custodian (DDL) | `/worktree` |
| sentinel + verifier | `/multitask` post-builder |
| T4 swarm | Cloud handoff + `/multitask` |
| Premium repair | `/best-of-n` (Human auth per ADR 0010) |

## T3+ path triggers

Pay/compliance → counsel (readonly). `lib/copilot/**` → ai_governance_reviewer + sentinel. See manifest `pathTriggers`.

## CI

`npm run governance:ci` on PRs. ADRs: [0010](../../specs/alignment/decisions/0010-agent-risk-tier-governance.md), [0011](../../specs/alignment/decisions/0011-function-lane-orchestration.md).

Precedence: Human PO → PO checkpoint → counsel → Security merge bar.
